# Claude Code local git worktrees — scaffolding, never committed. (Tracked
# .claude/settings.json + .claude/skills/ are intentional; only worktrees are
# local.) They were once committed as bare submodule gitlinks, which made every
# `actions/checkout` post-step warn `git ... exit code 128` (no .gitmodules).
.claude/worktrees/

